    "Datasets Our experiments are conducted on three recent long document summarization datasets: Multi-LexSum (ML, Shen et al., 2022), eLife (Goldsack et al., 2022) and BookSum Chapter (BC, Kryscinski et al., 2022).",
    "Parser For automatic parsing of source documents, we employ DMRST parser (Liu et al., 2020 (Liu et al.,, 2021)) which enables us to extract probabilities or uncertainties of discourse relations and type labels from its final logits layer."
